{"tid":1615344,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Tom Holland促成《蜘蛛俠》回歸MCU 借粉絲熱情融化堅冰","createTime":"2019-10-03T05:13:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T13:12:56.000Z","uid":49391,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"a967d1483ae4d5f03325cf9dd6ae4f8984c43e93","tid":1615344,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T05:13:05.000Z","msg":"在27號，索尼漫威講和，《蜘蛛俠》重返MCU。而據外媒The Hollywood Reporter報導，促成這一決議的即是蜘蛛俠的演員：Tom Holland，他曾向迪士尼/索尼影業的老總多次請求，最終讓蜘蛛俠得以重返MCU。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VjmztrV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVjmztrV.png&h=db88d3f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n時間回到8月25日，Holland曾在迪士尼的D23 Expo意外現身，獲得了粉絲們熱情歡呼。當時，大量標有#SaveSpiderMan的Tag在推特上瘋狂湧現。在這之後，Holland就開始了他的&ldquo;外交&rdquo;計劃。他向索尼和迪士尼展示了這些粉絲們的不斷湧出的期待，雙方緊張的關係開始隨之緩和。<br />\n<br />\n  最終，雙方達成了和解，並且漫威工作室和其主席凱文&middot;費奇將會聯手打造第三部《蜘蛛俠：返校季》系列電影，仍然會由湯姆&middot;霍蘭德主演。這部影片計劃於2021年7月16日正式上映，敬請期待。"},{"pid":"ec145c19941440e5af61ff3ee0dece9714dceceb","tid":1615344,"uid":49391,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T05:13:47.000Z","msg":"扮到好瀟灑咁,原來咁著緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01a8207e9e31ae2817fd4160c8a9b23a7bc17358","tid":1615344,"uid":197477,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T05:14:16.000Z","msg":"最大贏家：Tom Holland"},{"pid":"79a751c7bbad2574188f43450216f0dec01bd17c","tid":1615344,"uid":222907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T05:16:59.000Z","msg":"賺片酬姐"},{"pid":"e890728ed734567db139e1bf19fac48253a7cea3","tid":1615344,"uid":87757,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ec145c19941440e5af61ff3ee0dece9714dceceb","tid":1615344,"uid":49391,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T05:13:47.000Z","msg":"扮到好瀟灑咁,原來咁著緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T05:28:17.000Z","msg":"長拍長有 比你都著緊啦"},{"pid":"6c